WEBVTT

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.856
As a witness,

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:05.840
the war felt like history unfolding.

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:09.560
The government denied
that it was committing any violence,

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:13.416
but I continually drove through towns

00:04:13.440 --> 00:04:16.416
where people described
government massacres

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:18.959
from a day or a week before.

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.440
I felt overwhelmed

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:24.960
and tried to calm myself.

